In more detail, for $Î±_1 := a_{11} = 1$, $ğ¯_1 := A[2:3,1] = \vectt[2,1]$, $ğ°_1 = A[1,2:3] = \vectt[1,1]$ and
$$
K_1 := A[2:3,2:3] = \begin{bmatrix} 4 & 8 \\ 4 & 9 \end{bmatrix}
