we have
$$
A_2 := K_1 -ğ¯_1ğ°_1^âŠ¤ /Î±_1 = \begin{bmatrix} 4 & 8 \\ 4 & 9 \end{bmatrix} - \begin{bmatrix} 2 & 2 \\ 1 & 1 \end{bmatrix} = \begin{bmatrix} 2 & 6 \\ 3 & 8 \end{bmatrix}.
$$
We then repeat the process and determine (with $Î±_2 := A_2[1,1] = 2$, $ğ¯_2 := A_2[2:2,1] = [3]$, $ğ°_2 := A_2[1,2:2] = [6]$ and $K_2 := A_2[2:2,2:2] = [8]$):
